accTitle: Mermaid activations
accDescr {
Demonstrates explicit Mermaid activation control and activation shortcuts.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/05-activations/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/05-activations
}
